Modular version of the instructor's solution to assignment 1.  Note
the single header file block_manager.h coupled with two alternate
implementations in block_manager_vector.cc (original) and
block_manager_file.cc (low-level file I/O version).

Note that the main program is completely unmodified and word_counter.h
had a minor change (BLOCK_SIZE was moved to the newly-created
block.h).


In building the file version, a couple of minor bugs in block-handling
were identified and repaired
